ActAppropriation Act No. 3, 2006-2007
PrecisAppointment of RUTH ARCHIBALD as High Commissioner for Canada to the Kingdom of Lesotho, with residence in Pretoria; DENIS KINGSLEY as Commissioner for Canada to the British Territories of the Cayman Islands and to the Turks and Caicos Islands, with residence in Kingston; JEAN-PIERRE LAVOIE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Central African Republic and to the Republic of Chad, with residence in Yaounde; and MARIE-ISABELLE MASSIP as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Liberia and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Sierra Leone, with residence in Abidjan.
